name: 幸运公鸡八号 (Lucky Rooster #eight)
description:
公雞報曉意味著天明，象徵黑暗離去，光明到來，因此古代不少圖案中雄雞和太陽總是一起出現。當然雄雞也象徵守信準時。 

The rooster announces the dawn, which means the dawn, which symbolizes the departure of darkness and the arrival of light. Therefore, in many ancient patterns, the rooster and the sun always appear together. Of course, the rooster also symbolizes trustworthiness and punctuality.
